---
import AboutHeroImage from '../../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Ainnc"
	description="Ainnc is a bulk operations console for social media teams, covering accounts, proxies, assets, tasks, and usage limits."
	pubDate={new Date('July 03 2026')}
	category="Ainnc"
	tags={['Product', 'Operations', 'Social Media']}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
	locale="en"
>
	<p>
		Ainnc is a bulk operations console for social media teams. It brings account management,
		proxy IPs, file assets, task publishing, and usage limits into one workflow.
	</p>

	<p>
		Teams can import accounts, bind devices, upload videos and images, and complete publishing,
		login, and account warming tasks for platforms such as TikTok, Instagram, Reddit, and X.
	</p>

	<p>
		This blog documents product updates, tutorials, operating scenarios, and common questions so
		teams can build repeatable bulk operations workflows faster.
	</p>
</Layout>
